Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright and \Nsit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:13.26,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,My Future Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:19.23,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Hamakaze Elementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My future dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grade 1, Peach Class, Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of whether it \Nis a weekday or a Sunday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my parents are always lying \Naround, doing nothing at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father works on self-realization
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my mother is intent on capturing \Nthe dream of spinning reels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father said, "If we win it big, \Nwe'll take a trip to Hawaii!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my mother laughed, "They \Nwon't issue passports to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"so we won't be able to do that, hahaha."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there is never-ending \Nlaughter in my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, my future dream is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:57.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if it's because of what I was \Ntold yesterday at the Miss's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your life is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...utterly meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, pull yourself together! I \Nmade up my mind, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I don't yet know what \Nthe meaning of my life is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that for now, I'm just \Ngoing to protect the Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:21.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:25.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:29.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:31.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who is there to support his mistress \Nin all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:33.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:37.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is about a boy who fights and puts \Nhis life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:41.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Hayate Ayasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm going to \Nwork hard again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:54.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:54.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:02:01.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:02:01.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:04.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:04.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:09.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:09.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:13.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:13.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:22.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:22.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:25.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:25.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:32.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:32.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:38.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:38.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:41.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:41.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:45.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:45.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:50.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:50.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:57.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:57.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:04.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:04.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:20.44,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,265)}Long Ago, We Learned from a Space Sheriff \Nthat Being Young is About Not Looking Back
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? My future dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, if I had to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worry ceaselessly about what kind of \Nadult a certain girl will grow up to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I suppose you could say my dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that she becomes a respectable \Nmember of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you suddenly bring this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person's dream is sort of like the \Ndriving force behind his life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I-I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait. But according to that logic,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:56.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the driving force behind my \Nlife seems a bit questionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Ryoma Sakamoto said,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:04:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"As human beings, we ought to have \Ndreams as huge as the Pacific Ocean."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mozart was also vocal about how "life \Nis brilliant because we dream".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The lives of those incapable of \Nbig dreams must be like garbage,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is another quote from a certain \Nspy for the British Empire...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, somehow, I'm starting to feel \Never so slightly depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hayate, you really are \Nbehaving a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that Nagi's grandfather \Nsaid something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, it's important to always \Nremember one's initial enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I just plan to continue \Nto work hard for the Miss's sake
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the true Hayate Ayasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get any sleep at all because \Nof what happened yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone... who tries to make you cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would that... be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When all's said and done, \NHayate is still just so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate is working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:13.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about initial enthusiasm \Nbeing important and future dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate said that? What future dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's suddenly become like a salaryman, \Nwho's rediscovered life,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's been working furiously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:31.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be for our future together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't think that's quite right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's good, but I'm \Nnot ready for it yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Nagi, do you happen to have \Nsome kind of dream for the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure, it's normal to have lots, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, I intend to become a manga \Nauthor and sell a trillion copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, I just find you too brilliant \Nto look upon right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:06:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, but I wonder what \Nexactly is Hayate's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea. He was \Nstressing it quite a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he must have a really \Nbig dream of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:10.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Nagi, the dream you're \Nenvisioning right now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:13.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is almost certainly not the same \Nas the dream Hayate has in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:18.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, what in the world \Ncould Hayate's dream be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? My dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that was youthful \Nand rash, if you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty huge dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm embarrassed to \Neven say it out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't laugh or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 3LDK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.98,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(112,68)}Japanese 6 Tatami
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.98,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,251)}Western 4.5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 3LDK!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:48.12,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Hamakaze Elementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, my future dream is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to have a house with three rooms \Nin addition to a large space
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that serves as a living room, \Ndining room, and kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:55.66,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,My Future Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:07:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to live in this 3LDK in peace, \Nwithout fear of being driven out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's enough. You can stop now, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason for that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.20,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sense of Respect
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see. So your dream is a 3LDK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! D-Do you think that's a bit too big?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally fine it it's not inside Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bigger the dream the \Nmore wonderful it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, your cell \Nphone is still broken, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is inconvenient, so please \Ngo buy one on the expense account.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, understood. Then I'll go right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, also, it's important to \Ntake a break once in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please feel free to take \Nthe rest of the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go hang out \Nin town for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the opportunity to \Nbuy a really nice one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so this is 1seg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even make video calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I can enter up to 1000 \Naddresses. That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not that I need it. I \Ndon't have that many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I wonder how \Neveryone's doing back in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,School, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have time for it, so I \Ncompletely neglected to go, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right, I paid for \Nthe full tuition, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...want to go back to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.85,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Shiomi Municipal High School
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of let the moment \Ncarry me all the way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm finding it hard to actually go in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I should technically \Nstill be a student here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just go in boldly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! But I'm by \Nno means anyone suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Nishizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We haven't seen each other since Christmas.\N What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Souya and the others were worried, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you haven't been to school at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, a lot of things happened \Nsince the end of last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:08:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, how should I explain this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, my parents suddenly got \Ninto enormous debt and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I sort of got gifted to some "very \Ngenerous people" as collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.93,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(465,46)}Father
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.93,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(554,67)}Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, so with all the things that happened, \NI'm working as a butler at a certain mansion now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, come on, is that a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awful, Hayate. Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got to see you for \Nthe first time this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, i-i-it's nothing. I didn't \Nmean anything by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing flirting out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Souya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! It's Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were rumors that you'd quit school...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like I actually quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you, Nishizawa. You've \Ngot your beloved prince back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:10:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying? You \Nmust be an idiot, Souya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to worry \Nabout a classmate, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-For all that, you were on the verge \Nof tears when you heard he'd quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miss Nishizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're my classmate! Of \Ncourse, I was worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in that case, maybe I'll do \Nmy best to attend school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying, Ayasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been disenrolled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it's all right for a \Nteacher to utter such a flippant lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this, Nishizawa. \NI merely spoke the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki's parents came around \Nnoon on Christmas Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and demanded the rest of the tuition because \Nhe wouldn't be coming to school anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tuition? Didn't you pay it \Nout of your own pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because your parents \Nwouldn't pay it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you returned the money and \Ndisenrolled him? That's too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:54.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, but his parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:53.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I can't go to school, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're really going \Nto just disappear like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you raise the issue with the board \Nof education or something, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I did that, the teachers will \Nend up being held responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for my parents' selfish acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is farewell, Miss Nishizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:30.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was short, but... Farewell, \Nmy high school years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this to be good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So won't you please go out with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the moment that she said that, \NI came to a strange realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:56.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:12:00.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}without thinking, her face \Nflashed before my mind's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:10.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More than anything, I was struck by the \Nterribly sad expression on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you please go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm only interested in \Nthe 2-dimensional world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.72,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(488,112)}Crushed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke. But right now, \Nthere's someone I can't abandon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:37.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being fundamentally bad \Nat dealing with girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:40.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hayate believed it was more manly to refuse
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in a way that would make \Nher hate him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:46.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The protagonist of a comedic anime \Nnever gets dumped in a cool way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I heard you bought a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see it for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:09.40,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\fad(500,0)\pos(155,105)}Nagi Sanzenin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! I entered myself as the number \None entry in your address book!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm! E-mail me or call \Nme as much as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, I haven't given up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Lady, you better pay for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soft rice cake with strawberry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream of spinning is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.09,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Video Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Wataru, I finished watching \Nthis, so I'm returning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so what did you think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I guess I'd give it about 60 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I? That it's not \Na film a girl would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I'm at an age where I'd like \Nto learn what boys are thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can learn what boys are \Nthinking through monster films?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miss Nishizawa, this person \Nyou cared for quit school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! His house was gone and \Nthere were no clues to go on, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I wanted to see \Nhim one more time and talk to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way you'll ever find someone who's \Ngone missing like that, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you say something \Nso depressing, Wataru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.26,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru Only
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Wataru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't usually watch these anime, \Nbut are they interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything on that shelf are shows \Nthat I thought were interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know if you'll agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "what" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen here! Ultimately, whether you \Nthink it's interesting is subjective!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where you go with this, you won't know \Nunless you check it out with your own eyes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So quit complaining and watch it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:40.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use your head and judge for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:43.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether that is something you \Nfind truly interesting or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Coach for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's rented out right \Nnow, so start with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lunar Rabbit Weapon..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:51.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bamboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! That bamboo seller's \Nalways interrupting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:54.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bamboo poles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just remembered something \NI have to do, so I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bamboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! She ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to value our \Ncustomers a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, do you think it's possible to \Nfind a missing person in this big city?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been a truly wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru, I finished watching \Nthis, so I'm returning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, butler-in-debt, what \Ndid you think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found the life lessons it presented \Nto be quite informative,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems the Miss \Nfound it dissatisfactory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:25.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two keep missing each \Nother repeatedly. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki asked me to get a \Nvideo for him, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Is that Hayate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting him in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be we're destined to be together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be \Ngetting all sentimental!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate! Haya...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast. There's just no \Nway I can catch up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I have to keep up, so I \Ndon't lose sight of him at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he finally stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or wait, could it be that he lives here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?! It's more \Nlike a mansion than a house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Hayate doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate said something about \Nbeing collateral for debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, this must \Nbe a Yakuza residence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Hayate's being treated \Nin horrible ways in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:33.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What is this?! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we have a word with you in the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon? A girl who appears to \Nbe a suspicious individual?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought perhaps she could be \None of the Miss's acquaintances,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:40.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was hoping to get confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough guys in black! These \Npeople really {\i1}are{\i0} Yakuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, they're going to do things to me \Nthat will be unsuitable for a younger audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:53.79,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Shiomi High School
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a public high school bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that girl be from Hayate's old school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let go! Come on, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, she doesn't seem to be suspicious, \Nso please let go of her arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let her arms go for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I didn't tell you to let her get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies. We will catch her right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to escape somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have absolutely no \Nidea where Hayate might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Yakuza sure are impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Wataru wouldn't believe me even if I \Ntold him that they have a great mansion like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I have to find Hayate \Nquickly and escape with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:45.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Comedic depiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:48.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Realistic depiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why is there a tiger \Nat a Japanese residence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seriously going to die at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's chasing after me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I chasing after that girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the hunting instinct \Nthat I thought I'd lost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll follow that instinct
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and lick her all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:13.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You! That's a different kind of instinct!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lightning Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is a lethal technique \Nthat can only be mastered
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:28.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}by those who have overcome adversity \Nwith hard work and determination!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I haven't had any special \Ntraining or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Causing nothing but \Ntrouble, the same as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot. I'm being influenced by the \NDVDs I've borrowed from Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That technique name just slipped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what I meant when I talked \Nabout instructive life lessons...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Miss Nishizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so glad! It {\i1}is{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's hurry up and \Nescape from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:08.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is something that can \Nbe determined at a glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, who is this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is Miss Nishizawa and \Nshe used to be my classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, who is this little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is Miss Nagi and \Nshe's this estate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:30.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is a woman's intuition that \Neven the youngest girls have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:34.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her destined opponent, with whom she \Nwould fight over one precious thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:37.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One look, and they each \Nrecognized it instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That they were rivals!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! My backer's a hamster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it got eaten! So weak! \NMy hamster's so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll back down for today,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but next time, I'll bring a \Nstronger hamster with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Nishizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still the same old funny \Nperson, that Miss Nishizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, okay? You can't leave \Nme and go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nowhere else for \Nme to go except here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some who can't go to school \Nanymore, even if they want to, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Nagi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate has been good to me in so many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As his mistress, I must repay his devotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:29.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Nagi has made up her \Nmind about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time, he will be fighting \Nthe giant campus once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:34.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the meantime, aside from that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to rent these for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks for your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! "Cup-and-Ball and Carrot" is out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it got rented out just earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andarta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:50.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wataru's video store is \Ngetting a lot of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also currently offering 50% off rentals!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:57.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Moshi boku no yume ga kimi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:57.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If my dreams have taken your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:02.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kizutsuke-tetara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:02.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And brought it pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:08.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sono omoi wa itsuka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:08.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:11.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boku ga morau yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:11.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take from you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:17.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Taisetsu na mono ni furue-nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:17.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While trembling over something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:23.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kakezuri-mawatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:23.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And madly dashing about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:29.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seou itami ni hibi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:29.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The hurt I bore made the days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:33.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muimi ni sugita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:33.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Go by emptily
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.53,0:22:39.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oikaketa mama de oikosare-tsuzuke
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.53,0:22:39.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just chasing and continually being overtaken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:44.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tohou ni kureru kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:44.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A wind who's lost its bearing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.31,0:22:49.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi no doko ni furetara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.31,0:22:49.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of you should I touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:55.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ii ka o sagashita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:55.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I sought it out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.78,0:23:00.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mamoritai yo kimi dake wa tsuyoku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.78,0:23:00.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You alone, I want to protect so much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:05.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yokubou no wadachi kara touzakatte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:05.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting away from the rut of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:10.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Itsuka subete te ni ireru sore ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:10.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, it will all be ours and that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:14.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi to boku no Proof
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:14.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is our proof, yours and mine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:25.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Namida mo zenbu azukeru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:25.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even all my tears, I entrust to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:27.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:28.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:30.62,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,240)}Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:32.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Hayate Ayasaki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.85,0:23:33.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nagi Sanzenin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:35.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:38.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be doing this segment with \Nthe Miss's song in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:42.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. As the Sanzenin family heir, the \Nability to sing is an important factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.24,0:23:46.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It fully reflects how you are a spoiled, \Nunmanageable bundle of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.33,0:23:47.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A true masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.39,0:23:49.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Was that \Nintended as a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:50.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:53.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The song vibrantly conveys how \Ncute you are, if you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.02,0:23:54.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute?! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:56.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:59.38,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,240)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:24:00.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, some documents have \Narrived from Hakuou Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:19.43,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.13,0:24:02.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The transfer application, right? For you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.09,0:24:03.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.36,0:24:05.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What do you mean, for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.08,0:24:07.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,They're transfer documents for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:10.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I shall relate the story \Nof my entrance exam experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.09,0:24:13.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you the Hakuou entrance exam \Ntrends and how to deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.75,0:24:15.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.29,0:24:17.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:19.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Hear That Those Who Rule the \NSummer Rule at Entrance Exams".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:22.40,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,I Hear That Those Who Rule the \NSummer Rule at Entrance Exams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.77,0:24:21.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I{\i0} saw the promise in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:23.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go to school together!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.13,0:24:24.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Run up to that arena of your dreams!
